My First Development!
So far this is what i have done. they will be more to come. UPDATES: Full dds speced no delay adding mage/range/melle following barrage instant freeze/multi barrage Magic hovering fun-pk Admin-Mod Cp Panel.
UPDATES TO COME?! Skillscape emotes. diffrent sprites of magic A donator skill no delay on teleports. And more.
ANCHOR. The reason i only took of weilding is because i can't be botherd to do a 10 second video of the running/spec/attack. but they are all correct apart from 1 little thing. on the special it dont have the gold around the anchor. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2euj1u8.png[/img]
All the correct ancients/Hovering [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/24cy6ia.png[/img]

New Teleport. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/35lu39k.png[/img]
Modern Magic with donator teleport and hovering. [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/314bawz.png[/img]
New Shop Interfaces. [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/10hokyb.png[/img]
Better training with new rat looks :d [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/25qf901.png[/img]
New Monk Robes. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2d0xgd5.png[/img]
PvP Armors And Ava's/Godsword Shards. Speak to person to trade them in for a godsword. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/1447039.png[/img]
Full Ringmaster [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/30k8yvs.png[/img]
The Correct models for dragon'hai robes! [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2lw6cex.png[/img]
